HEADWORD: Stagecoach
<hw>Stage"coach`</hw> <pr>(st⟦amac⟧j"k⟦omac⟧ch`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A coach that runs regularly from one stage, station, or place to
another, for the conveyance of passengers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

